name: Temple
description: "This mysterious temple (found upon a mountain which seems to defy all laws of physics by being a floating mass of land...) from hell is like no other, it does not play by the rules of logic or reason, other dimensions are tearing through the very walls of this monstrosity. But they are the least of your concern, the real issue is that you need to get out of this hellhole!" This is a MAP22 replacement for Final Doom: TNT Evilution, it focuses on both exploration and ammo conservation, my advice is to get the blue key from the right section of the map and then head into the left (you will need that key, trust me you will need it), however what you do first is optional...
